==Introduction==
The '''Help''' component displays contextual help information for the user.

The following help information is provided:
* tooltips for the form fields (instructions how to enter information for particular property)
* Concept Help pages (summary of the Concept purpose, structure and restrictions)


==Definition==
<pre>
<properties>
  <property name="{NAME}">
    <instruction>{EDIT INSTRUCTION}</instruction>
  </property>
  <property name="{PROPERTY}">
    <instruction>{EDIT INSTRUCTION}</instruction>
  </property>
</properties>
</pre>

{| class="helptable"
|-
! {NAME}
| A name of the Property
|-
! {EDIT INSTRUCTION}
| An edit instructions for given property. This content is displayed as a tooltip for the form field associated with the property.
|}



==Example==
<pre>
<properties>
  <property name="Description" type="Text" label="Description" attribute="description">
    <description>A free text format to describe the purpose, relevance and functionality of a certain entity.</description>
    <instruction>A "Description" is a text value that reflects a short explanation for a taxonomy element. </instruction>
  </property>
</properties>
</pre>


==User Interface==
The help information is provided in the:
* Edit and Search Pages (tooltips for each form field)
* User Manual pages

